00:00:11.302 --> 00:00:12.762 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
Wha--? What the--?

00:00:12.846 --> 00:00:14.723 position:50% align:center
But I just went...

00:00:14.806 --> 00:00:18.601 position:50% align:center
Ah! That's more like it.
Now to find Tesla!

00:00:18.685 --> 00:00:23.523 position:50% align:center
[screams] Why're you watching me
drop the kids off at the pool?

00:01:59.202 --> 00:02:01.079 position:50% align:center
Reona, help me! Now! Please?

00:02:01.162 --> 00:02:05.333 position:50% align:center
This one's way too big
to handle on my own!

00:02:05.417 --> 00:02:09.170 position:50% align:center
Uh. I'm sure it's fine?
Just remember not to strain.

00:02:09.254 --> 00:02:10.714 position:50% align:center
I believe in you!

00:02:10.797 --> 00:02:15.343 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] It's gonna rip me
in half! [screams]

00:02:16.177 --> 00:02:17.971 position:50% align:center
[HIRO gasping]

00:02:20.140 --> 00:02:21.891 position:50% align:center
[yelps]

00:02:21.975 --> 00:02:24.769 position:50% align:center
Thank goodness! Are you okay?

00:02:24.853 --> 00:02:27.022 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
What the hell?

00:02:27.105 --> 00:02:30.900 position:50% align:center
I-- I mean. How'd you
even know I was here?

00:02:30.984 --> 00:02:33.278 position:50% align:center
I followed you. When you
dove into the crap house

00:02:33.361 --> 00:02:36.531 position:50% align:center
it struck me as the perfect
time to observe!

00:02:36.614 --> 00:02:39.117 position:50% align:center
I was keen on watching
you in action again,

00:02:39.200 --> 00:02:42.746 position:50% align:center
but then all of a sudden
a nasty old goblin

00:02:42.829 --> 00:02:45.081 position:50% align:center
went and beat me to the punch!

00:02:45.165 --> 00:02:50.378 position:50% align:center
He was too fixated to see
me, so off with his head!

00:02:50.462 --> 00:02:51.796 position:50% align:center
Another one for the pile!

00:02:51.880 --> 00:02:54.382 position:50% align:center
Lucky for us he was
preoccupied, huh?

00:02:54.466 --> 00:02:57.510 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] Problematic,
but I suppose I'll take it.

00:02:57.594 --> 00:02:59.387 position:50% align:center
Um, thank you, I guess?

00:02:59.471 --> 00:03:02.557 position:50% align:center
Hey, no problem, happy to help.
Quick question, though.

00:03:02.640 --> 00:03:04.601 position:50% align:center
Have you been taking
care of your sword?

00:03:04.684 --> 00:03:07.187 position:50% align:center
Don't want it gettin' all
sorts-a rusty on you.

00:03:07.270 --> 00:03:09.147 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
It's good. No worries.

00:03:09.230 --> 00:03:13.276 position:50% align:center
I'm sure you think so,
but I'd better have a look.

00:03:14.277 --> 00:03:16.696 position:50% align:center
Huh...

00:03:16.780 --> 00:03:18.156 position:50% align:center
Heh!

00:03:18.239 --> 00:03:20.700 position:50% align:center
Uh-- I--

00:03:20.784 --> 00:03:25.080 position:50% align:center
[screams] Son of a whore!
Why would you do that?

00:03:25.163 --> 00:03:29.751 position:50% align:center
[laughs] I adore how easy it is
to get a reaction out of you!

00:03:29.834 --> 00:03:32.462 position:50% align:center
You're every Inquisitor's
dream come true!

00:03:32.545 --> 00:03:34.964 position:50% align:center
Oh, Hiro. Fruit girl's MIA.

00:03:35.048 --> 00:03:37.967 position:50% align:center
We're alone.
Let me see your O face!

00:03:38.051 --> 00:03:41.221 position:50% align:center
And by "O," I mean "Ow."

00:03:41.304 --> 00:03:46.726 position:50% align:center
No! You're insane. This has
to be your idea of a joke.

00:03:46.810 --> 00:03:49.437 position:50% align:center
[MIZARISA]
Now, now. It won't be all pain.

00:03:49.521 --> 00:03:51.731 position:50% align:center
I can do pleasure, too, ya know.

00:03:51.815 --> 00:03:54.901 position:50% align:center
Forget it, I'm not falling for
the naughty girl act again.

00:03:54.984 --> 00:03:59.406 position:50% align:center
[MIZARISA]
It's not an act. Here, see?

00:03:59.489 --> 00:04:01.116 position:50% align:center
Ta-da!

00:04:01.199 --> 00:04:02.283 position:50% align:center
[HIRO gasps]

00:04:02.367 --> 00:04:05.161 position:50% align:center
[MIZARISA]
Go ahead. Grab on.

00:04:05.245 --> 00:04:09.499 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] Ugh! Seriously,
18-plus mode kicks in now?

00:04:09.582 --> 00:04:11.584 position:50% align:center
Horrible timing!

00:04:13.253 --> 00:04:14.004 position:50% align:center
[HIRO gasps]

00:04:14.087 --> 00:04:15.338 position:50% align:center
[MIZARISA]
Huh?

00:04:16.047 --> 00:04:18.258 position:50% align:center
If you lovebirds
are done being gross,

00:04:18.341 --> 00:04:19.968 position:50% align:center
the city of Ted
just happens to be

00:04:20.051 --> 00:04:22.595 position:50% align:center
in the middle of a goblin siege.

00:04:22.679 --> 00:04:25.890 position:50% align:center
So go make 'em a peach cobbler
and stop ruining the moment!

00:04:25.974 --> 00:04:28.518 position:50% align:center
Yeah? Hey, why don't I
use your sweetbreads!

00:04:28.601 --> 00:04:30.061 position:50% align:center
Bring it, tramp!

00:04:30.145 --> 00:04:33.440 position:50% align:center
Oh, honey. You couldn't find my
sweetbreads with a road atlas!

00:04:33.523 --> 00:04:36.526 position:50% align:center
Stop! Both of you!
This is ridiculous!

00:04:36.609 --> 00:04:39.029 position:50% align:center
We need to track down Tesla!
Get a grip!

00:04:39.112 --> 00:04:41.906 position:50% align:center
If the goblins find us here,
we're screwed!

00:04:41.990 --> 00:04:43.742 position:50% align:center
[MIZARISA] Wait!
Don't just take off during!

00:04:43.825 --> 00:04:44.784 position:50% align:center
I haven't finished!

00:04:44.868 --> 00:04:47.537 position:50% align:center
[ALICIA]
It's kind of his thing.

00:04:51.875 --> 00:04:53.043 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
Who am I kidding?

00:04:53.126 --> 00:04:54.502 position:50% align:center
Those two'll skin me
alive before

00:04:54.586 --> 00:04:56.379 position:50% align:center
the goblins have
the opportunity!

00:04:56.463 --> 00:04:59.090 position:50% align:center
Hell, death by goblin is
probably the better option!

00:04:59.174 --> 00:05:02.093 position:50% align:center
Knock it off! Think positive!

00:05:03.386 --> 00:05:04.554 position:50% align:center
What the hell, Reona?

00:05:04.637 --> 00:05:06.306 position:50% align:center
Didn't you hear me
screaming earlier?

00:05:06.389 --> 00:05:09.642 position:50% align:center
Mizarisa stabbed me after
a goblin watched me poop!

00:05:09.726 --> 00:05:12.645 position:50% align:center
Sorry. Had a lot to
contend with myself.

00:05:12.729 --> 00:05:15.231 position:50% align:center
Huh? So, what was
going on with you?

00:05:15.315 --> 00:05:17.108 position:50% align:center
Look. Do you see this?

00:05:17.192 --> 00:05:19.319 position:50% align:center
I have more split ends
than a fork.

00:05:19.402 --> 00:05:20.904 position:50% align:center
Are you kidding me?

00:05:20.987 --> 00:05:23.948 position:50% align:center
You're supposed to help me beat
this, not obsess over your hair!

00:05:24.032 --> 00:05:25.158 position:50% align:center
[stomach grumbling]

00:05:25.241 --> 00:05:26.534 position:50% align:center
Work with me here.

00:05:26.618 --> 00:05:29.162 position:50% align:center
Come on. No way is
there anything left.

00:05:29.245 --> 00:05:32.165 position:50% align:center
Uh... The game might be
picking up on your anxiety

00:05:32.248 --> 00:05:35.043 position:50% align:center
and generating a situation that
forces you to deal with it.

00:05:35.126 --> 00:05:38.129 position:50% align:center
Great! And it thinks
this is a good time?

00:05:38.213 --> 00:05:39.506 position:50% align:center
Damn it. Ugh.

00:05:39.589 --> 00:05:42.967 position:50% align:center
I don't need a pipe-bursting
case of nerves again.

00:05:43.051 --> 00:05:45.220 position:50% align:center
"Again"? What does that mean?

00:05:45.303 --> 00:05:48.306 position:50% align:center
Ugh. Forget it, okay?

00:05:48.390 --> 00:05:52.352 position:50% align:center
No. That isn't healthy.
You need to talk this out.

00:05:52.435 --> 00:05:54.688 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
But the goblins? Hello?

00:05:54.771 --> 00:05:56.439 position:50% align:center
That's the point
I'm trying to make!

00:05:56.523 --> 00:05:58.274 position:50% align:center
You can't beat the goblins
if you don't

00:05:58.358 --> 00:06:01.027 position:50% align:center
process your trauma! Tell me.

00:06:01.111 --> 00:06:03.655 position:50% align:center
Look, I promise
it's not a big deal.

00:06:03.738 --> 00:06:06.408 position:50% align:center
Hiro, I'm not some stupid brat.

00:06:06.491 --> 00:06:09.536 position:50% align:center
Whatever your secret,
you can trust me to be mature.

00:06:09.619 --> 00:06:13.415 position:50% align:center
I won't make fun of you.

00:06:13.498 --> 00:06:17.502 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] All right, then.
Brace yourself.

00:06:17.585 --> 00:06:21.381 position:50% align:center
[laughing]

00:06:21.464 --> 00:06:23.049 position:50% align:center
You tripped and peed your pants

00:06:23.133 --> 00:06:25.260 position:50% align:center
in front of a stadium
full of people!

00:06:25.343 --> 00:06:27.345 position:50% align:center
That's hilarious!

00:06:27.429 --> 00:06:29.514 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
Oh, yeah! Real mature!

00:06:29.597 --> 00:06:32.308 position:50% align:center
You're the last person
I should've told!

00:06:32.392 --> 00:06:35.145 position:50% align:center
KQ doesn't skimp on
the psychological angle.

00:06:35.228 --> 00:06:37.814 position:50% align:center
If a real-life event left
a scar on your psyche,

00:06:37.897 --> 00:06:39.816 position:50% align:center
it's gonna have an
in-game counterpart.

00:06:39.899 --> 00:06:41.818 position:50% align:center
Every time you face
the moment of truth,

00:06:41.901 --> 00:06:42.986 position:50% align:center
you'll have to poop.

00:06:43.069 --> 00:06:45.780 position:50% align:center
I didn't poop myself,
I just peed!

00:06:45.864 --> 00:06:47.157 position:50% align:center
[REONA]
Potato, potato.

00:06:47.240 --> 00:06:49.576 position:50% align:center
The specific details really
aren't that important.

00:06:49.659 --> 00:06:51.911 position:50% align:center
Easy for you to say!
While we're on the subject,

00:06:51.995 --> 00:06:54.330 position:50% align:center
could you please stop talking
about bathroom functions?

00:06:54.414 --> 00:06:58.293 position:50% align:center
Whatever. You think I'm bad?
Imagine how Kamui would spin it.

00:06:58.376 --> 00:07:02.297 position:50% align:center
"Boo-hoo. Quit whining and
steer into the skid, IBS boy.

00:07:02.380 --> 00:07:05.717 position:50% align:center
Gonna run away, might
as well leave a trail. Die."

00:07:05.800 --> 00:07:08.303 position:50% align:center
I didn't poop myself--
I just peed!

00:07:08.386 --> 00:07:11.765 position:50% align:center
I can't believe we're
having this conversation!

00:07:11.848 --> 00:07:13.516 position:50% align:center
[REONA]
Hey. How's the tummy?

00:07:13.600 --> 00:07:17.520 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] Hm? Whoa. I think
the spasms are gone.

00:07:17.604 --> 00:07:18.396 position:50% align:center
[REONA laughs]

00:07:18.480 --> 00:07:20.023 position:50% align:center
Wait a second, you...

00:07:20.106 --> 00:07:22.734 position:50% align:center
Did you wind me up
like that on purpose?

00:07:22.817 --> 00:07:25.570 position:50% align:center
I suppose that depends
on whether it helped.

00:07:25.653 --> 00:07:28.406 position:50% align:center
Well, yeah. It did.

00:07:28.490 --> 00:07:32.452 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] There was probably a more
humane way, but whatever.

00:07:32.535 --> 00:07:33.828 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:07:33.912 --> 00:07:35.497 position:50% align:center
[REONA]
Ooo! A new title!

00:07:35.580 --> 00:07:38.375 position:50% align:center
Wha...? Again with the timing.

00:07:38.458 --> 00:07:44.255 position:50% align:center
[REONA] "Evacuation Best Friend
Killer: Bowel-Emptying Amicide."

00:07:44.339 --> 00:07:45.882 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] Ah! How many times
do I have to say

00:07:45.965 --> 00:07:47.676 position:50% align:center
I didn't poop myself?

00:07:47.759 --> 00:07:49.010 position:50% align:center
[REONA]
Never mind.

00:07:49.094 --> 00:07:50.595 position:50% align:center
Now that waste management
is no longer an issue,

00:07:50.679 --> 00:07:52.013 position:50% align:center
let's get to the North Gate.

00:07:52.097 --> 00:07:53.473 position:50% align:center
If my hunch is correct,
that's where

00:07:53.556 --> 00:07:55.350 position:50% align:center
Alicia and Mizarisa are headed.

00:07:55.433 --> 00:07:56.893 position:50% align:center
Right! We, uh...

00:07:56.976 --> 00:07:59.729 position:50% align:center
Tesla needs all
the help he can get!

00:08:07.904 --> 00:08:10.448 position:50% align:center
[TESLA] Don't lose heart.
Stay focused, men.

00:08:10.532 --> 00:08:11.908 position:50% align:center
[GUARDS]
Yes, sir!

00:08:14.285 --> 00:08:15.370 position:50% align:center
[GOBLINS grunt]

00:08:15.453 --> 00:08:18.289 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] Oh, no.
One goblin is bad enough.

00:08:18.373 --> 00:08:21.376 position:50% align:center
This many can take out
the whole city!

00:08:21.459 --> 00:08:23.753 position:50% align:center
Not even Tesla stands a chance!

00:08:23.837 --> 00:08:24.963 position:50% align:center
Forward!

00:08:25.046 --> 00:08:30.885 position:50% align:center
[GUARDS yelling]

00:08:32.053 --> 00:08:35.056 position:50% align:center
[GUARD A groans]

00:08:35.140 --> 00:08:37.892 position:50% align:center
[GUARDS groaning]

00:08:37.976 --> 00:08:39.310 position:50% align:center
[GUARD D grunting]

00:08:39.394 --> 00:08:42.814 position:50% align:center
Extreme Lighting!

00:08:42.897 --> 00:08:46.985 position:50% align:center
[GOBLINS groaning]

00:08:47.068 --> 00:08:51.239 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] Granted, he is amazing.
But no one can do this alone.

00:08:51.322 --> 00:08:53.742 position:50% align:center
[MIZARISA screams]

00:08:53.825 --> 00:08:56.369 position:50% align:center
[GOBLIN E groans]

00:08:56.453 --> 00:08:59.497 position:50% align:center
Mizarisa? That's the second
one you've killed tonight!

00:08:59.581 --> 00:09:01.332 position:50% align:center
Yeah. Try not to be
too impressed,

00:09:01.416 --> 00:09:03.543 position:50% align:center
it's all by the skin
of my teeth.

00:09:03.626 --> 00:09:05.587 position:50% align:center
[GOBLIN B growls]

00:09:05.670 --> 00:09:07.547 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:09:07.630 --> 00:09:10.425 position:50% align:center
Watermelon... Split!

00:09:10.508 --> 00:09:13.261 position:50% align:center
[GOBLIN B groaning]

00:09:13.345 --> 00:09:15.555 position:50% align:center
[roaring]

00:09:15.638 --> 00:09:18.099 position:50% align:center
Chopping Apples!

00:09:18.183 --> 00:09:20.727 position:50% align:center
[ALICIA yelling]

00:09:23.063 --> 00:09:27.525 position:50% align:center
Ah--well okay, then.
They're, uh, seriously strong.

00:09:27.609 --> 00:09:31.404 position:50% align:center
Extreme Lightning!

00:09:31.488 --> 00:09:33.615 position:50% align:center
[GOBLINS groaning]

00:09:33.698 --> 00:09:38.328 position:50% align:center
Ha! Say your prayers! [laughs]

00:09:38.411 --> 00:09:39.746 position:50% align:center
[GOBLIN J roars]

00:09:39.829 --> 00:09:41.998 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:09:42.082 --> 00:09:46.211 position:50% align:center
[GOBLIN J groaning]

00:09:46.294 --> 00:09:47.921 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
Hmm...

00:09:48.004 --> 00:09:51.675 position:50% align:center
[MIZARISA giggles]

00:09:51.758 --> 00:09:53.259 position:50% align:center
[ALICIA yelling]

00:09:55.136 --> 00:09:57.722 position:50% align:center
Real talk, this is
a phenomenal team.

00:09:57.806 --> 00:09:59.516 position:50% align:center
Look at 'em do their thing!

00:09:59.599 --> 00:10:01.935 position:50% align:center
You may actually clear
this stage after all!

00:10:02.018 --> 00:10:05.230 position:50% align:center
I know, right?
This is incredible!

00:10:05.313 --> 00:10:07.982 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] Sweet! As long
as Tesla stays alive,

00:10:08.066 --> 00:10:12.362 position:50% align:center
the odds of me surviving
are looking pretty good!

00:10:12.445 --> 00:10:13.738 position:50% align:center
I have news!

00:10:13.822 --> 00:10:15.615 position:50% align:center
The goblins have just
breached the southern gate.

00:10:15.699 --> 00:10:18.368 position:50% align:center
Queen Govern's estate is
under attack as I speak!

00:10:18.451 --> 00:10:19.953 position:50% align:center
What? But how?

00:10:20.036 --> 00:10:23.039 position:50% align:center
