The guards I stationed there

00:10:23.123 --> 00:10:25.375 position:50% align:center
were given strict orders
to hold the line!

00:10:25.458 --> 00:10:26.960 position:50% align:center
I know, sir.

00:10:27.043 --> 00:10:30.338 position:50% align:center
