goblin managed to push through.

00:10:30.422 --> 00:10:32.340 position:50% align:center
The guards were all...

00:10:32.424 --> 00:10:36.177 position:50% align:center
[TESLA]
Oh... One Eye.

00:10:36.261 --> 00:10:38.388 position:50% align:center
Uh. Is that a name?

00:10:38.471 --> 00:10:41.975 position:50% align:center
[TESLA] I'll explain later,
Hiro. To Queen Govern's at once!

00:10:42.058 --> 00:10:43.435 position:50% align:center
[GUARDS]
Sir!

00:10:43.518 --> 00:10:45.478 position:50% align:center
[HIRO gasps]

00:10:45.562 --> 00:10:47.147 position:50% align:center
[CATHY groaning]

00:10:47.230 --> 00:10:49.691 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
A-Are you guys hurt?

00:10:49.774 --> 00:10:53.778 position:50% align:center
We'll be okay.
But Amos and Palù are gone.

00:10:53.862 --> 00:10:58.033 position:50% align:center
[gasps] That's terrible!

00:10:58.116 --> 00:11:00.744 position:50% align:center
I wasn't their biggest fan,
but still...

00:11:00.827 --> 00:11:03.830 position:50% align:center
When the goblins showed up,
the two of them went AWOL.

00:11:03.913 --> 00:11:05.915 position:50% align:center
Because of course they did.

00:11:05.999 --> 00:11:08.668 position:50% align:center
Join Tesla! There aren't
many guards left standing!

00:11:08.752 --> 00:11:11.463 position:50% align:center
By the time he gets there,
he'll be fighting alone!

00:11:11.546 --> 00:11:14.049 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
Uh-- I'm on it!

00:11:17.719 --> 00:11:19.262 position:50% align:center
[HIRO gasps]

00:11:19.346 --> 00:11:20.805 position:50% align:center
[GUARD E groans]

00:11:20.889 --> 00:11:23.224 position:50% align:center
[GUARDS groaning]

00:11:23.308 --> 00:11:30.023 position:50% align:center
[ONE-EYE roars]

00:11:30.106 --> 00:11:32.359 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
What the hell is that?

00:11:32.442 --> 00:11:35.987 position:50% align:center
Behold. The king of the goblins.

00:11:37.447 --> 00:11:39.574 position:50% align:center
[TESLA]
One Eye.

00:11:44.579 --> 00:11:48.958 position:50% align:center
[ONE-EYE growling]

00:11:49.042 --> 00:11:51.461 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] All right.
Guess this guy explains

00:11:51.544 --> 00:11:54.631 position:50% align:center
why the odds of
survival are 0.1.

00:11:54.714 --> 00:11:59.427 position:50% align:center
I've faced him before.
We fought several years ago.

00:11:59.511 --> 00:12:02.180 position:50% align:center
Goblins were said to be
testing the perimeter.

00:12:02.263 --> 00:12:04.933 position:50% align:center
I was dispatched to investigate.

00:12:05.016 --> 00:12:05.934 position:50% align:center
[ONE-EYE groans]

00:12:06.017 --> 00:12:07.644 position:50% align:center
[TESLA]
Though I pierced his eye,

00:12:07.727 --> 00:12:12.023 position:50% align:center
it took everything
I had to escape.

00:12:12.107 --> 00:12:15.151 position:50% align:center
The cage! Have it
brought here at once!

00:12:15.235 --> 00:12:16.361 position:50% align:center
[GUARDS]
Sir!

00:12:16.444 --> 00:12:17.696 position:50% align:center
[HIRO gasps]

00:12:17.779 --> 00:12:19.406 position:50% align:center
[TESLA]
Hiro.

00:12:21.241 --> 00:12:24.369 position:50% align:center
Stand firm. Have heart.

00:12:24.452 --> 00:12:26.079 position:50% align:center
When One Eye is vanquished,

00:12:26.162 --> 00:12:29.124 position:50% align:center
we may venture beyond
the city gate arm-in-arm!

00:12:29.207 --> 00:12:31.418 position:50% align:center
Whoa! Why would you say that?

00:12:31.501 --> 00:12:35.130 position:50% align:center
Seriously, man!
That's dead guy talk!

00:12:36.506 --> 00:12:38.299 position:50% align:center
[TESLA]
Harken, foul beast!

00:12:38.383 --> 00:12:41.636 position:50% align:center
The man who stands before
you gave you your name!

00:12:41.720 --> 00:12:45.432 position:50% align:center
[ONE-EYE growls]

00:12:45.515 --> 00:12:47.392 position:50% align:center
[ONE-EYE roars]

00:12:47.475 --> 00:12:50.562 position:50% align:center
Um. Okay, he's alarmingly fast.

00:12:50.645 --> 00:12:53.773 position:50% align:center
[TESLA grunting]

00:12:53.857 --> 00:12:56.401 position:50% align:center
Get it together. C'mon.

00:12:57.902 --> 00:13:00.280 position:50% align:center
[HIRO whimpers]

00:13:02.532 --> 00:13:03.700 position:50% align:center
Don't worry, love.

00:13:03.783 --> 00:13:05.785 position:50% align:center
Let the qualified
warriors handle it.

00:13:05.869 --> 00:13:07.579 position:50% align:center
Focus on keeping
your pants clean.

00:13:07.662 --> 00:13:10.373 position:50% align:center
Could you maybe not joke about
that right now, please?

00:13:10.457 --> 00:13:12.917 position:50% align:center
[laughs] Fun and games aside,

00:13:13.001 --> 00:13:15.045 position:50% align:center
you really ought
to sit this one out.

00:13:15.128 --> 00:13:17.130 position:50% align:center
It's phenomenally dangerous.

00:13:17.213 --> 00:13:19.132 position:50% align:center
Yeah, I'm aware, but I--

00:13:19.215 --> 00:13:23.553 position:50% align:center
[ALICIA] She's right. Stand back
and let us do our thing.

00:13:23.636 --> 00:13:25.597 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
Alicia? You...

00:13:25.680 --> 00:13:28.058 position:50% align:center
Captain Tesla is our
beacon of hope.

00:13:28.141 --> 00:13:31.686 position:50% align:center
I will not allow him to perish
at the hands of a goblin!

00:13:31.770 --> 00:13:34.898 position:50% align:center
Nobly said. Goodness.
For a knife-wielding freakshow,

00:13:34.981 --> 00:13:38.526 position:50% align:center
you certainly have a
knack for eloquence.

00:13:38.610 --> 00:13:42.155 position:50% align:center
[gasps] Did these two
bury the hatchet?

00:13:42.238 --> 00:13:45.575 position:50% align:center
Not sure how that happened,
but I'll take it!

00:13:45.658 --> 00:13:47.827 position:50% align:center
Hey, Hiro. Did I hear correctly?

00:13:47.911 --> 00:13:50.205 position:50% align:center
Tesla barked an order
about some sort of cage?

00:13:50.288 --> 00:13:54.292 position:50% align:center
Yeah. Must be important,
'cause he wanted it here fast.

00:13:54.376 --> 00:13:56.378 position:50% align:center
Sounds to me like
obvious foreshadowing,

00:13:56.461 --> 00:13:58.463 position:50% align:center
unless I'm wrong. But you know,

00:13:58.546 --> 00:14:00.757 position:50% align:center
the cage might just signify
that the battle's over,

00:14:00.840 --> 00:14:03.134 position:50% align:center
which means if we hold out,
we'll have won!

00:14:03.218 --> 00:14:04.761 position:50% align:center
I guess that makes sense.

00:14:04.844 --> 00:14:09.849 position:50% align:center
Hold fast, Captain Tesla!
Your reinforcements are here!

00:14:09.933 --> 00:14:11.017 position:50% align:center
[MIZARISA laughing]

00:14:11.101 --> 00:14:13.687 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] Come on, Mizarisa!
You can do it!

00:14:13.770 --> 00:14:15.563 position:50% align:center
[MIZARISA groans]

00:14:20.777 --> 00:14:22.862 position:50% align:center
Mizarisa!

00:14:25.699 --> 00:14:27.242 position:50% align:center
Probably not as bad as it looks!

00:14:27.325 --> 00:14:29.536 position:50% align:center
I think she's just been
knocked unconscious.

00:14:29.619 --> 00:14:31.788 position:50% align:center
Whew. Well, that's
something at least.

00:14:31.871 --> 00:14:34.499 position:50% align:center
Sure, she's a total
psychopath, but still.

00:14:34.582 --> 00:14:36.501 position:50% align:center
What happened exactly?

00:14:36.584 --> 00:14:41.131 position:50% align:center
Ugh. That beast kicked
Mizarisa in the abdomen.

00:14:41.214 --> 00:14:44.467 position:50% align:center
Looks like I'm up.

00:14:44.551 --> 00:14:46.386 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
Be careful!

00:14:51.558 --> 00:14:55.061 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] Um. I have no earthly
idea what's going on.

00:14:55.145 --> 00:14:56.354 position:50% align:center
[REONA]
Yeah. Me neither.

00:14:56.438 --> 00:14:58.273 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
Of course.

00:14:58.356 --> 00:15:01.985 position:50% align:center
Kinda feels like they cheaped
out on the big climax. I mean,

00:15:02.068 --> 00:15:05.613 position:50% align:center
shouldn't the protagonist
be able to see the action?

00:15:05.697 --> 00:15:08.825 position:50% align:center
Look! We're almost to the end!

00:15:10.201 --> 00:15:13.413 position:50% align:center
Hell yeah! Sweet!
Bring on the cage!

00:15:13.496 --> 00:15:16.624 position:50% align:center
Wait, what?

00:15:16.708 --> 00:15:19.794 position:50% align:center
[cries]

00:15:20.795 --> 00:15:24.257 position:50% align:center
[HIRO gasping]
Why do we have goblins?

00:15:24.341 --> 00:15:26.217 position:50% align:center
[GUARD H] They're all part
of the Captain's plan!

00:15:26.301 --> 00:15:28.636 position:50% align:center
When One Eye sees them,
he'll recoil and falter.

00:15:28.720 --> 00:15:31.681 position:50% align:center
Then the advantage will be ours!

00:15:33.600 --> 00:15:39.022 position:50% align:center
[TESLA] Lo! You recognize
your own, do you not? Observe!

00:15:40.690 --> 00:15:43.902 position:50% align:center
[GOBLIN CHILDREN crying]

00:15:43.985 --> 00:15:45.862 position:50% align:center
[ONE-EYE roars]

00:15:45.945 --> 00:15:47.280 position:50% align:center
Cool! It's working!

00:15:47.364 --> 00:15:48.740 position:50% align:center
So, they have intelligence?

00:15:48.823 --> 00:15:50.492 position:50% align:center
Never saw that comin'.

00:15:50.575 --> 00:15:51.910 position:50% align:center
[TESLA growls]

00:15:53.078 --> 00:15:57.165 position:50% align:center
[ONE-EYE screams]

00:15:58.166 --> 00:16:00.377 position:50% align:center
[GOBLIN CHILDREN crying]

00:16:02.754 --> 00:16:04.798 position:50% align:center
It's over now. You're done.

00:16:04.881 --> 00:16:08.093 position:50% align:center
All right! Safe to say
the tide's finally turned!

00:16:08.176 --> 00:16:11.888 position:50% align:center
It really has! You're about to
clear the goblin siege of Ted!

00:16:11.971 --> 00:16:16.559 position:50% align:center
Dude! We actually just beat
a 0.1 chance of survival!

00:16:16.643 --> 00:16:18.520 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
Well, to be fair.

00:16:18.603 --> 00:16:22.357 position:50% align:center
Kamui was laying
it on pretty thick.

00:16:22.440 --> 00:16:27.362 position:50% align:center
[KAMUI]
Chance of survival, 0.1%. Die.

00:16:27.445 --> 00:16:29.447 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
Hold on. That doesn't track.

00:16:29.531 --> 00:16:31.658 position:50% align:center
Kamui's a jerk, but why
make a walkthrough

00:16:31.741 --> 00:16:33.702 position:50% align:center
if it only helps players
figure out you lied about

00:16:33.785 --> 00:16:35.870 position:50% align:center
the game's difficulty?

00:16:35.954 --> 00:16:37.455 position:50% align:center
[KAMUI]
But once you've cleared it,

00:16:37.539 --> 00:16:40.625 position:50% align:center
you'll get at the real mystery
behind the City of Ted.

00:16:40.709 --> 00:16:45.922 position:50% align:center
Keep your mouth shut,
eyes open, and your mind alert.

00:16:46.006 --> 00:16:47.590 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
Where's the "real" mystery?

00:16:47.674 --> 00:16:49.884 position:50% align:center
And keep my mind alert for what?

00:16:49.968 --> 00:16:52.971 position:50% align:center
Was he just grandstanding?
Come on, think!

00:16:53.054 --> 00:16:54.305 position:50% align:center
[GOBLIN CHILDREN wailing]

00:16:54.389 --> 00:16:57.017 position:50% align:center
Could you be quiet?
I'm trying to work this out!

00:16:57.100 --> 00:17:00.895 position:50% align:center
Hey. Wait. I've heard
this sound before!

00:17:00.979 --> 00:17:01.855 position:50% align:center
[PRISONER B wailing]

00:17:01.938 --> 00:17:03.273 position:50% align:center
[HIRO gasps]

00:17:03.356 --> 00:17:07.235 position:50% align:center
[PRISONER A groaning]

00:17:08.737 --> 00:17:13.491 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] Can't be! That's insane!
But I know what I heard.

00:17:13.575 --> 00:17:14.617 position:50% align:center
[TESLA yelling]

00:17:14.701 --> 00:17:17.037 position:50% align:center
Tesla! Hold on!

00:17:18.079 --> 00:17:22.042 position:50% align:center
What's the matter with you?
Why would you stay my hand?

00:17:22.125 --> 00:17:25.045 position:50% align:center
I-- Where'd these
guys come from?

00:17:25.128 --> 00:17:27.672 position:50% align:center
Were they captured
during the siege?

00:17:27.756 --> 00:17:29.924 position:50% align:center
Or have they been here a while?

00:17:30.008 --> 00:17:32.302 position:50% align:center
Did you abduct them?

00:17:32.385 --> 00:17:35.555 position:50% align:center
Did you hit your head?
Don't get uppity with Tesla!

00:17:35.638 --> 00:17:37.349 position:50% align:center
First you can't
control your bowels,

00:17:37.432 --> 00:17:39.225 position:50% align:center
now you've lost
your grasp of reality!

00:17:39.309 --> 00:17:41.019 position:50% align:center
Do me a quick favor
and stop talking.

00:17:41.102 --> 00:17:42.437 position:50% align:center
[REONA]
Ow!

00:17:42.520 --> 00:17:44.647 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] This isn't the first time
I've heard them crying.

00:17:44.731 --> 00:17:46.733 position:50% align:center
I noticed the sound
while I was in prison.

00:17:46.816 --> 00:17:48.902 position:50% align:center
Then again after
I started training.

00:17:48.985 --> 00:17:51.863 position:50% align:center
They were there as I watched
Ginji being carted off, too.

00:17:51.946 --> 00:17:53.656 position:50% align:center
Originally, I figured
it had to be someone

00:17:53.740 --> 00:17:55.492 position:50% align:center
really dangerous being
kept out of sight,

00:17:55.575 --> 00:17:57.702 position:50% align:center
but I couldn't have
been more wrong.

00:17:57.786 --> 00:18:01.289 position:50% align:center
These poor creatures
were crying out for help!

00:18:01.373 --> 00:18:02.624 position:50% align:center
You've had them tucked away

00:18:02.707 --> 00:18:05.919 position:50% align:center
since well before
all this began!

00:18:06.002 --> 00:18:06.878 position:50% align:center
They're pale.

00:18:06.961 --> 00:18:08.129 position:50% align:center
They're half blind.

00:18:08.213 --> 00:18:09.756 position:50% align:center
Their voices are strained.

00:18:09.839 --> 00:18:11.549 position:50% align:center
All signs they've
been kept in the dark

00:18:11.633 --> 00:18:14.469 position:50% align:center
way longer than the siege
has been going on.

00:18:14.552 --> 00:18:16.930 position:50% align:center
In fact, I'd say all
things considered,

00:18:17.013 --> 00:18:19.766 position:50% align:center
they must've been
here for years!

00:18:19.849 --> 00:18:22.769 position:50% align:center
Only one person could
orchestrate that,

00:18:22.852 --> 00:18:24.646 position:50% align:center
and that's you!

00:18:24.729 --> 00:18:26.815 position:50% align:center
Bravo! Brilliant deduction!

00:18:26.898 --> 00:18:29.526 position:50% align:center
Too bad this is an RPG
and not a mystery!

00:18:29.609 --> 00:18:32.487 position:50% align:center
Get your head in the game!
Stop overthinking!

00:18:32.570 --> 00:18:34.447 position:50% align:center
What would conceivably
possess Tesla to--

00:18:34.531 --> 00:18:36.950 position:50% align:center
[ONE-EYE growling]

00:18:39.035 --> 00:18:40.662 position:50% align:center
[BOTH gasp]

00:18:46.668 --> 00:18:48.920 position:50% align:center
[GOBLIN CHILDREN scream]

00:18:49.004 --> 00:18:50.422 position:50% align:center
Wha--? Why would you...?

00:18:50.505 --> 00:18:54.592 position:50% align:center
Damn it! I told you to hold off!
Have you lost your mind?!

00:18:55.719 --> 00:18:58.138 position:50% align:center
[TESLA]
You're full of surprises, Hiro.

00:18:58.221 --> 00:19:01.433 position:50% align:center
And far more clever
than I suspected.

00:19:01.516 --> 00:19:02.934 position:50% align:center
[HIRO gasping]

00:19:03.018 --> 00:19:06.563 position:50% align:center
[TESLA] Your surmise is correct.
I kidnapped them.

00:19:06.646 --> 00:19:09.649 position:50% align:center
Seven years ago, give or take.

00:19:09.733 --> 00:19:12.944 position:50% align:center
And to make matters
even more interesting,

00:19:13.028 --> 00:19:16.489 position:50% align:center
this wretched creature
was their father.

00:19:17.991 --> 00:19:20.243 position:50% align:center
Wow, that's dark.

00:19:20.326 --> 00:19:23.455 position:50% align:center
But why, Captain Tesla,

00:19:23.538 --> 00:19:26.791 position:50% align:center
how could you do
something so wicked?

00:19:31.796 --> 00:19:33.506 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
Uh-oh.

00:19:37.510 --> 00:19:39.596 position:50% align:center
Queen Govern!

00:19:45.769 --> 00:19:48.438 position:50% align:center
Well, then. It appears
you've slayed him.

00:19:48.521 --> 00:19:51.649 position:50% align:center
Indeed. I'm afraid
I had no choice.

00:19:51.733 --> 00:19:54.736 position:50% align:center
No matter. Tis easily remedied.

00:19:54.819 --> 00:19:58.865 position:50% align:center
Why, the offspring of some
other goblin can be snatched.

00:19:58.948 --> 00:20:00.450 position:50% align:center
[HIRO whimpering]

00:20:00.533 --> 00:20:03.912 position:50% align:center
Majesty. Why sanction
such a heinous act?

00:20:03.995 --> 00:20:05.914 position:50% align:center
Because there is
no greater method

00:20:05.997 --> 00:20:10.168 position:50% align:center
for keeping our citizenry in
check than fear of the outside.

00:20:10.251 --> 00:20:12.170 position:50% align:center
You mean, we--

00:20:12.253 --> 00:20:14.339 position:50% align:center
It's all politics.

00:20:14.422 --> 00:20:15.840 position:50% align:center
[QUEEN GOVERN]
Dear child...

00:20:15.924 --> 00:20:19.177 position:50% align:center
We are beyond the control
of every kingdom in Auberdine.

00:20:19.260 --> 00:20:20.845 position:50% align:center
For all intents and purposes,

00:20:20.929 --> 00:20:23.682 position:50% align:center
a nation state with
complete autonomy.

00:20:23.765 --> 00:20:26.935 position:50% align:center
The pristine City of Ted.

00:20:27.018 --> 00:20:28.353 position:50% align:center
What's more,

00:20:28.436 --> 00:20:31.981 position:50% align:center
goblins are a characteristically
peace-loving species.

00:20:34.693 --> 00:20:37.320 position:50% align:center
[TESLA] They are a distinct
culture unto themselves.

00:20:37.404 --> 00:20:42.575 position:50% align:center
Unless provoked, they rarely,
if ever, attack human beings.

00:20:42.659 --> 00:20:44.744 position:50% align:center
However, their penchant
for ferocity

00:20:44.828 --> 00:20:49.708 position:50% align:center
when cornered can be quite
useful when channeled properly.

00:20:49.791 --> 00:20:53.128 position:50% align:center
Not only are they an effective
tool for keeping people out,

00:20:53.211 --> 00:20:58.925 position:50% align:center
they're absolutely marvelous at
keeping adventuresome fools in.

00:20:59.009 --> 00:21:00.885 position:50% align:center
Indeed, they're
the perfect means

00:21:00.969 --> 00:21:02.929 position:50% align:center
with which to rule
our citizens.

00:21:03.013 --> 00:21:05.098 position:50% align:center
Thus is the fate of
these pitiful souls

00:21:05.181 --> 00:21:07.392 position:50% align:center
at the hands of their betters.

00:21:07.475 --> 00:21:08.977 position:50% align:center
Quite. You could say

00:21:09.060 --> 00:21:12.147 position:50% align:center
they're the foundation
on which the city is built.

00:21:16.192 --> 00:21:17.694 position:50% align:center
That bastard!

00:21:17.777 --> 00:21:20.280 position:50% align:center
I've crushed on him since
I was in high school!

00:21:20.363 --> 00:21:23.742 position:50% align:center
Clearly, it's time to reconsider
my taste in hot guys.

00:21:23.825 --> 00:21:25.744 position:50% align:center
Kamui should've
been that revelation.

00:21:25.827 --> 00:21:27.787 position:50% align:center
You're like a
barometer for jerks.

00:21:27.871 --> 00:21:30.331 position:50% align:center
No one asked you!

00:21:33.376 --> 00:21:35.003 position:50% align:center
Crap!

00:21:35.086 --> 00:21:36.212 position:50% align:center
[swords clanging]

00:21:36.296 --> 00:21:39.132 position:50% align:center
[GUARDS groan]

00:21:40.550 --> 00:21:44.346 position:50% align:center
Uh! Tesla! You straight up
murdered your own men!

00:21:44.429 --> 00:21:47.057 position:50% align:center
I've no choice when
faced with exposure.

00:21:47.140 --> 00:21:48.975 position:50% align:center
Ted's secret must be kept safe.

00:21:49.059 --> 00:21:52.062 position:50% align:center
Anyone unlucky enough
to discover has to die.

00:21:52.145 --> 00:21:53.980 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:21:54.064 --> 00:21:58.651 position:50% align:center
[TESLA] You do realize
of course, you're next.

00:21:58.735 --> 00:22:02.906 position:50% align:center
[HIRO] Thundering Tesla, the
toughest NPC in the game...

00:22:02.989 --> 00:22:05.283 position:50% align:center
I get it now.

00:22:05.367 --> 00:22:08.453 position:50% align:center
The only way out of here
is by defeating him.

00:22:08.536 --> 00:22:13.875 position:50% align:center
That 0.1 chance of survival
suddenly makes a lot more sense.

00:23:45.842 --> 00:23:49.304 position:50% align:center
[HIRO]
Episode 12: "RealityxVR."